Environment Setup


-----------------




-----------------




-----------------




-----------------




-----------------



1. Copy the example environment file::

      cp .env.example .env

2. Edit the configuration::

      Required API keys
      OPENAI_API_KEY=your_key_here
      TWELVE_LABS_API_KEY=your_key_here

      Optional settings
      MAX_CONCURRENT_JOBS=3
      CACHE_TTL=86400

See :doc:`/getting_started` to begin using the system.

